  F --> G[/tasks default landing route]
  B -- Yes --> G
  G --> H[Shared shell navigation]
  H --> I[/tasks list]
  H --> J[/tasks?view=board]
  H --> K[/overview/pm]
  H --> L[/inbox/:role]
  H --> M[/tasks/:taskId]
